[src:symfony/page-creation] *Create a route*: The route defines the URL path to your page and what controller method to call.
[src:symfony/page-creation] You'll learn more about routing in its own section, including how to make *variable* URLs.
[src:symfony/page-creation] Your project already has a powerful debugging tool inside: the `bin/console` command.
